To keep your email address anonymous and unlinked from your Prolific ID, *please send an email to **[study+alena@alena.com](mailto:study+alena@alena.com)*. (You can do this by clicking on the email address, or copy-pasting it into your email app)

*Please do this now*, and then come back here and proceed with the survey.
